Dialogue: 1,0:19:50.74,0:19:54.16,IN-EN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(240,240)\3c&HF98412&\blur3}But now you’re going to leave with nothing but a sign
Dialogue: 1,0:19:58.52,0:20:05.13,IN-EN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(240,240)\3c&HF98412&\blur3}Another evening I’ll be sitting reading in between your lines
Dialogue: 1,0:20:06.17,0:20:08.69,IN-EN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(240,240)\3c&HF98412&\blur3}Because I miss you all the time
Dialogue: 1,0:20:11.95,0:20:14.18,IN-EN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(240,240)\3c&HF98412&\blur3}So, get away
